{"tid":2183631,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE泳裝「濕身蜜桃翹臀」漏餡！","createTime":"2020-09-01T04:57:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T07:22:10.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8000050924b26210a75b1a57ec7990fef544d166","tid":2183631,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:57:55.000Z","msg":"南韓日前再度爆發新冠肺炎疫情後，多名影視從業人員確診，藝人們人人自危，各電視台節目、劇組陸續停工，TWICE的子瑜近日便發文向粉絲求推薦，希望網友能分享最喜歡的電影、電視劇，看來要開啟追劇模式了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5110/d5110685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5110%2Fd5110685.jpg&h=77cc4b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜曬舊照。（圖／翻攝自TWICE IG）<br />\n<br />\n疫情的關係，很多人都無法出國旅遊，只能在社交平台上曬舊照回憶，子瑜也跟風分享3年前和成員的出遊照，其中一張和姐妹們在無邊際泳池邊跳望城市夜景，4人背影入鏡、穿著長袖泳衣，款式雖然保守，但其中一位成員撐在岸邊直起身體時，意外讓纖細腰身及蜜桃翹臀入鏡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5110/d5110684.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5110%2Fd5110684.jpg&h=bb664b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜抱著愛犬撒嬌。（圖／翻攝自TWICE IG）<br />\n<br />\n除了分享旅遊照，子瑜還同步求推薦，有台灣網友推薦上半年最紅的偶像劇《想見你》，還有人介紹近期熱門的電影《可不可以你也剛好喜歡我》，另外也有人推超夯韓劇《機智醫生生活》、《雖然是精神病但沒關係》給子瑜，滿足她的追劇需求。"},{"pid":"76d8a03ed19a668cded0efdb2a60a83cd8348ab1","tid":2183631,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:58:08.000Z","msg":"比想像中緊!"},{"pid":"5a71bb513e6f367967015a9b17a011f631eb5ca3","tid":2183631,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:05:41.000Z","msg":"中國戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af27c02112494b794e7e7f701202f9df29081d6b","tid":2183631,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ea4524186dc0204956da35f7c45f1fd86ede88","tid":2183631,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T07:22:10.000Z","msg":"要瘋狂狗仔式教訓下個衰妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}